# API vs Endpoint

| API | Endpoint |
|-----|----------|
| Complete communication interface | Specific URL inside an API |
| Contains multiple endpoints | Represents a single resource |

Example

Student API

Endpoints

GET /students

POST /students

PUT /students/1

DELETE /students/1

