# Common Interview Mistakes

❌ API and Endpoint are the same.

✅ An API contains one or more endpoints.

---

❌ JSON is a programming language.

✅ JSON is a data-interchange format.

---

❌ REST only supports JSON.

✅ REST can use JSON, XML, or other data formats.

---

❌ GET is used to create data.

✅ POST is used to create resources.

